--&gt;]&lt;/ref&gt;\
While\
most\
observers\
had,\
at\
the\
beginning\
of\
the\
talks,\
anticipated\
independence\
as\
the\
most\
likely\
outcome,\
others\
suggested\
that\
a\
rapid\
resolution\
might\
not\
be\
preferable.&lt;ref&gt;[http://www.ft.com/cms/s/985caa90-de5a-11db-afa7-000b5df10621.html\
